Definition: inflammation of the intestines caused by Endamoeba histolytica
Example: usually acquired by ingesting food or water contaminated with feces; characterized by severe diarrhea
Synonyms: amoebic_dysentery, amebiasis, dysentery, inflammation, of, the, intestines, caused, by, Endamoeba, histolytica, usually, acquired, ingesting, food, or, water, contaminated, with, feces, characterized, severe, diarrhea
Category: noun.state
